    "transcriptLines": [["00:00:00,000","00:00:28,280","You will hear a talk on New Zealand radio about an art sale which is being held to raise money for charity. First you have some time to look at questions 11 to 13."],["00:00:28,280","00:00:51,400","Now listen carefully and answer questions 11 to 13."],["00:00:51,400","00:00:58,760","One of the most anticipated art events in Christchurch is the charity art sale organised this year by Neil Curtis. Neil, tell us all about it."],["00:00:58,760","00:01:04,040","Well Diane, this looks like being the biggest art sale yet and the best thing about it is that the money raised will all go to charity."],["00:01:04,040","00:01:09,240","So what you probably want to know first is where it is. Well the pictures will be on view all this week, most of them at the star gallery in the shopping mall."],["00:01:09,240","00:01:14,600","But we have so many pictures this year that we're also showing some in the <span class='answer-highlight'>cafe</span> next door. So do drop in and see them any day between 9 and 5."],["00:01:14,600","00:01:20,120","Now if you're interested in buying rather than just looking and we hope a lot of you will be, the actual sale will take place on Thursday evening with sales starting at <span class='answer-highlight'>7.30</span>."],["00:01:20,120","00:01:26,040","Refreshments will be available before the sale starting at 6.30. We've got about 50 works by local artists showing a huge range of styles and media."],["00:01:26,040","00:01:31,800","You're probably also interested in what's going to happen to your money once you've handed it over. Well all proceeds will go to support children who are <span class='answer-highlight'>disabled</span> both here in New Zealand and also in other countries."],["00:01:31,800","00:01:39,320","Now let me tell you a bit about some of the artists who have kindly agreed to donate their pictures to the charity art sale."],["00:01:39,320","00:01:45,080","One of them is Don Stubley who has a special interest in the art sale because his five-year-old daughter was born with a serious back problem."],["00:01:45,080","00:01:51,400","After an operation earlier this year she's now doing fine but Don says he wants to offer something to help other less fortunate children."],["00:01:51,400","00:01:58,840","Don is totally self-taught and says he's passionate about painting. His paintings depict some of our New Zealand <span class='answer-highlight'>birds</span> in their natural habitats."],["00:01:58,840","00:02:04,840","One relative newcomer to New Zealand is James Chang who came here from Taiwan nine years ago at the age of 56."],["00:02:04,840","00:02:10,840","Mr Chang had 13 <span class='answer-highlight'>exhibitions</span> in Taiwan before he came to live here in Christchurch so he's a well-established artist."],["00:02:10,840","00:02:16,040","His paintings are certainly worth looking at. If you like <span class='answer-highlight'>abstract</span> pictures with strong color schemes you'll love them."],["00:02:16,040","00:02:22,600","Natalie Stevens was born in New Zealand but has exhibited in China, Australia and Spain. As well as being an artist she's a website <span class='answer-highlight'>designer</span>."],["00:02:22,600","00:02:28,600","She believes art should be universal and her paintings use soft colors in a mixture of media. Most of her pictures are <span class='answer-highlight'>portraits</span> so some of them may even be friends of yours."],["00:02:28,600","00:02:34,600","And then we have Christine Shin from Korea. Christine only started to learn English <span class='answer-highlight'>two years</span> ago when she arrived in New Zealand."],["00:02:34,600","00:02:40,600","She's been painting professionally for over 10 years and she sure knows how to communicate strong messages through the universal language of art."],["00:02:40,600","00:02:46,600","She usually works from <span class='answer-highlight'>photographs</span> and paints delicate watercolours which combine traditional Asian influences with New Zealand landscapes."],["00:02:46,600","00:02:52,600","That is the end of part two. You now have half a minute to check your answers."]],
